{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775877785906,"sessionID":"ses_285703b89ffecpRDQILMzEYYNL","part":{"id":"prt_d7a908916001ve3mbmr9PzDzNo","messageID":"msg_d7a901aaf001R3WeTuIJj5fFSn","sessionID":"ses_285703b89ffecpRDQILMzEYYNL","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-af16eebaed97413d9a3b6621e37885a0","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-028 — SDK AgentRuntimeClient Specification\n\n## Module: sdk-python\n\n### AgentRuntimeClient Class\n\n#### Constructor\n\n```python\nclass AgentRuntimeClient:\n    def __init__(\n        self,\n        base_url: str,\n        api_key: Optional[str] = None,\n        timeout: int = 30,\n        max_retries: int = 3\n    ) -> None\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `base_url`: Base URL of the AgentRuntime service\n- `api_key`: Optional API key for authentication\n- `timeout`: Request timeout in seconds (default: 30)\n- `max_retries`: Maximum number of retry attempts (default: 3)\n\n#### Agent Management Methods\n\n##### create_agent\n\n```python\nasync def create_agent(\n    self,\n    config: AgentConfig,\n    workspace_id: Optional[str] = None\n) -> Agent\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `config`: Agent configuration object\n- `workspace_id`: Optional workspace ID\n\n**Returns:** `Agent` object\n\n**Raises:** `AgentCreationError`, `AuthenticationError`, `ConnectionError`, `ValidationError`\n\n##### get_agent\n\n```python\nasync def get_agent(self, agent_id: str) -> Agent\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `agent_id`: ID of the agent\n\n**Returns:** `Agent` object\n\n**Raises:** `AgentNotFoundError`, `AuthenticationError`, `ConnectionError`\n\n##### list_agents\n\n```python\nasync def list_agents(\n    self,\n    workspace_id: Optional[str] = None,\n    status: Optional[AgentStatus] = None,\n    limit: int = 100,\n    offset: int = 0\n) -> List[Agent]\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `workspace_id`: Optional workspace ID to filter by\n- `status`: Optional agent status to filter by\n- `limit`: Maximum number of agents to return (default: 100)\n- `offset`: Pagination offset (default: 0)\n\n**Returns:** List of `Agent` objects\n\n**Raises:** `AuthenticationError`, `ConnectionError`\n\n##### update_agent\n\n```python\nasync def update_agent(\n    self,\n    agent_id: str,\n    config: AgentConfig\n) -> Agent\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `agent_id`: ID of the agent\n- `config`: Updated agent configuration\n\n**Returns:** Updated `Agent` object\n\n**Raises:** `AgentNotFoundError`, `AuthenticationError`, `ConnectionError`, `ValidationError`\n\n##### delete_agent\n\n```python\nasync def delete_agent(self, agent_id: str) -> None\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `agent_id`: ID of the agent\n\n**Raises:** `AgentNotFoundError`, `AuthenticationError`, `ConnectionError`\n\n#### Runtime Operations Methods\n\n##### start_agent\n\n```python\nasync def start_agent(\n    self,\n    agent_id: str,\n    input_data: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None\n) -> RuntimeSession\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `agent_id`: ID of the agent\n- `input_data`: Optional input data for the agent\n\n**Returns:** `RuntimeSession` object\n\n**Raises:** `AgentNotFoundError`, `RuntimeError`, `AuthenticationError`, `ConnectionError`\n\n##### stop_agent\n\n```python\nasync def stop_agent(\n    self,\n    session_id: str,\n    graceful: bool = True\n) -> None\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `session_id`: ID of the runtime session\n- `graceful`: Whether to stop gracefully (default: True)\n\n**Raises:** `SessionNotFoundError`, `RuntimeError`, `AuthenticationError`, `ConnectionError`\n\n##### get_session_status\n\n```python\nasync def get_session_status(self, session_id: str) -> RuntimeSession\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `session_id`: ID of the runtime session\n\n**Returns:** `RuntimeSession` object\n\n**Raises:** `SessionNotFoundError`, `AuthenticationError`, `ConnectionError`\n\n##### list_sessions\n\n```python\nasync def list_sessions(\n    self,\n    agent_id: Optional[str] = None,\n    status: Optional[SessionStatus] = None,\n    limit: int = 100,\n    offset: int = 0\n) -> List[RuntimeSession]\n```\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `agent_id`: Optional agent ID to filter by\n- `status`: Optional session status to filter by\n- `limit`: Maximum number of sessions to return (default: 100)\n- `offset`: Pagination offset (default: 0)\n\n**Returns:** List of `RuntimeSession` objects\n\n**Raises:** `AuthenticationError`, `ConnectionError`\n\n## Data Models\n\n### Agent\n\n```python\nclass Agent(BaseModel):\n    agent_id: str\n    workspace_id: str\n    name: str\n    description: Optional[str]\n    config: AgentConfig\n    status: AgentStatus  # Enum: CREATING, ACTIVE, STOPPED, ERROR, DELETED\n    created_at: datetime\n    updated_at: datetime\n    metadata: Dict[str, str]\n```\n\n### AgentStatus\n\n```python\nclass AgentStatus(str, Enum):\n    CREATING = \"creating\"\n    ACTIVE = \"active\"\n    STOPPED = \"stopped\"\n    ERROR = \"error\"\n    DELETED = \"deleted\"\n```\n\n### AgentConfig\n\n```python\nclass AgentConfig(BaseModel):\n    runtime_config: RuntimeConfig\n    capabilities: List[str]\n    constraints: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None\n    resources: Optional[ResourceConfig] = None\n```\n\n### RuntimeConfig\n\n```python\nclass RuntimeConfig(BaseModel):\n    type: str  # e.g., \"llm\", \"function\", \"hybrid\"\n    model_id: str\n    parameters: Dict[str, Any]\n```\n\n### ResourceConfig\n\n```python\nclass ResourceConfig(BaseModel):\n    cpu: Optional[str] = None\n    memory: Optional[str] = None\n    gpu: Optional[str] = None\n    timeout: Optional[int] = None\n```\n\n### RuntimeSession\n\n```python\nclass RuntimeSession(BaseModel):\n    session_id: str\n    agent_id: str\n    status: SessionStatus  # Enum: STARTING, RUNNING, COMPLETED, STOPPED, ERROR\n    input_data: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None\n    output_data: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None\n    started_at: datetime\n    completed_at: Optional[datetime] = None\n    error_message: Optional[str] = None\n```\n\n### SessionStatus\n\n```python\nclass SessionStatus(str, Enum):\n    STARTING = \"starting\"\n    RUNNING = \"running\"\n    COMPLETED = \"completed\"\n    STOPPED = \"stopped\"\n    ERROR = \"error\"\n```\n\n## Exception Hierarchy\n\n```\nAgentRuntimeException\n├── AuthenticationError\n├── ConnectionError\n├── AgentError\n│   ├── AgentCreationError\n│   ├── AgentNotFoundError\n│   └── AgentUpdateError\n├── RuntimeError\n│   ├── SessionNotFoundError\n│   └── RuntimeError as ExecutionError\n└── ValidationError\n```\n\n## HTTP Endpoints\n\n### Agent Endpoints\n\n- `POST /v1/agents` - Create agent\n- `GET /v1/agents/{agent_id}` - Get agent\n- `GET /v1/agents` - List agents\n- `PUT /v1/agents/{agent_id}` - Update agent\n- `DELETE /v1/agents/{agent_id}` - Delete agent\n\n### Runtime Endpoints\n\n- `POST /v1/agents/{agent_id}/start` - Start agent\n- `POST /v1/sessions/{session_id}/stop` - Stop agent\n- `GET /v1/sessions/{session_id}` - Get session status\n- `GET /v1/sessions` - List sessions","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-028/spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-028/spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-028/spec.md","time":{"start":1775877785897,"end":1775877785903}}}}
