{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775877815238,"sessionID":"ses_285703b89ffecpRDQILMzEYYNL","part":{"id":"prt_d7a90fbac001K04HiOK9r2PjKO","messageID":"msg_d7a90c65600138k2TFSHFm9kWr","sessionID":"ses_285703b89ffecpRDQILMzEYYNL","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-00b6439c9cb14a0ba08c27149b6af51c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-028 — SDK AgentRuntimeClient Delta Specification\n\n## Change Summary\n\nThis AR introduces a new SDK client for the AgentRuntime service, enabling Python applications to manage agents and their runtime sessions programmatically.\n\n## New API Endpoints\n\n### Agent Management\n\n- `POST /v1/agents` - Create a new agent\n- `GET /v1/agents/{agent_id}` - Retrieve agent details\n- `GET /v1/agents` - List agents with optional filtering\n- `PUT /v1/agents/{agent_id}` - Update agent configuration\n- `DELETE /v1/agents/{agent_id}` - Delete an agent\n\n### Runtime Operations\n\n- `POST /v1/agents/{agent_id}/start` - Start an agent execution session\n- `POST /v1/sessions/{session_id}/stop` - Stop a running session\n- `GET /v1/sessions/{session_id}` - Get session status and details\n- `GET /v1/sessions` - List sessions with optional filtering\n\n## New Data Models\n\n### Agent\n\n```python\n{\n  \"agent_id\": str,\n  \"workspace_id\": str,\n  \"name\": str,\n  \"description\": Optional[str],\n  \"config\": AgentConfig,\n  \"status\": AgentStatus,\n  \"created_at\": datetime,\n  \"updated_at\": datetime,\n  \"metadata\": Dict[str, str]\n}\n```\n\n### AgentConfig\n\n```python\n{\n  \"runtime_config\": RuntimeConfig,\n  \"capabilities\": List[str],\n  \"constraints\": Optional[Dict[str, Any]],\n  \"resources\": Optional[ResourceConfig]\n}\n```\n\n### RuntimeSession\n\n```python\n{\n  \"session_id\": str,\n  \"agent_id\": str,\n  \"status\": SessionStatus,\n  \"input_data\": Optional[Dict[str, Any]],\n  \"output_data\": Optional[Dict[str, Any]],\n  \"started_at\": datetime,\n  \"completed_at\": Optional[datetime],\n  \"error_message\": Optional[str]\n}\n```\n\n## New Enums\n\n### AgentStatus\n\n- `CREATING` - Agent is being created\n- `ACTIVE` - Agent is active and ready\n- `STOPPED` - Agent is stopped\n- `ERROR` - Agent encountered an error\n- `DELETED` - Agent has been deleted\n\n### SessionStatus\n\n- `STARTING` - Session is starting\n- `RUNNING` - Session is running\n- `COMPLETED` - Session completed successfully\n- `STOPPED` - Session was stopped\n- `ERROR` - Session encountered an error\n\n## New Exceptions\n\n### AgentRuntimeException (base)\n- `AuthenticationError` - Authentication failed\n- `ConnectionError` - Connection to service failed\n- `AgentError` (base)\n  - `AgentCreationError` - Failed to create agent\n  - `AgentNotFoundError` - Agent not found\n  - `AgentUpdateError` - Failed to update agent\n- `RuntimeError` (base)\n  - `SessionNotFoundError` - Session not found\n  - `ExecutionError` - Runtime execution failed\n- `ValidationError` - Input validation failed\n\n## Backward Compatibility\n\nThis change introduces entirely new functionality and does not modify existing APIs. It is fully backward compatible.\n\n## Migration Notes\n\nNo migration required. This is a new feature addition.\n\n## Dependencies\n\nThis change depends on:\n- `httpx` >= 0.24.0\n- `pydantic` >= 2.0.0\n- Python >= 3.9\n\n## Breaking Changes\n\nNone. This is a new feature.","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-028/delta-spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-028/delta-spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-028/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775877815232,"end":1775877815236}}}}
